content.content: 1. (1) The parks named in Column 1 of the Table are the provincial parks of Ontario. R.R.O. 1990, Reg. 951, s. 1 (1). (2) A provincial park consists of the land delimited or set aside for it, as described in the Schedule referred to in Column 2 of the Table or as described in section 2 of this Regulation. R.R.O. 1990, Reg. 951, s. 1 (2); O. Reg. 136/91, s. 1.
